were on the same floor, the top floor of old Francis 
Hall.

05:35.453 --> 05:46.505
And I often went to him with my problems

05:35.453 --> 05:46.505
and also helped him with some of his. So I got I 
should say I obtained quite a bit of formal

05:51.082 --> 06:02.615
parasitology without even realizing it.

06:02.635 --> 06:08.040
And often I would take his classes when he was ill or 
out of town or whatnot. And the more I

06:09.542 --> 06:19.553
delved into it, the more I became interested. 1938 
I

