The receiver was about three to six inches by an 
inch and a half and the battery pack weighed about a

06:38.819 --> 06:45.810
pound. So I had Johnny

06:52.405 --> 07:00.535
or what that Houston, Johnny Holly,

06:52.405 --> 07:00.535
built a harness for me.

