I was making $3,600 a year with the experiment 
station. The authority department was 4,500 so I

10:24.085 --> 10:31.836
took it with no regrets. Dr. Smith was rather 
impatient

10:33.378 --> 10:50.221
with me but after all I'd worked for him nine years 
and I decided I could handle teaching with a

10:33.378 --> 10:50.221
hearing aid. So then

10:56.570 --> 10:57.712
Things rocked along.

