important parts of the School of Veterinary

22:35.060 --> 22:48.732
Medicine because one of the main reasons it was 
founded was because of the parasitic problem with

22:35.060 --> 22:48.732
tick fever. That's right. And I saw the last group 
of cattle treated for tick fever over in

22:50.494 --> 23:03.345
Liberty County in 1936, shortly after I came here.

23:08.050 --> 23:11.894
